casebody.data:
No. 804

(October Term 1936).

Railroad Commission of California et al. v. Pacific Gas & Electric Co. October 11, 1937. Mr. Ira H. Rowell for appellants. Messrs. Warren Olney, Jr., Allan P. Matthew, and Robert L. Lipman for appellee.

The petition for rehearing in this case is granted and the case is restored to the docket and assigned for reargument.
